org.knime.base.data.aggregation.dialogutil

Interface AggregationFunctionRow<F extends AggregationFunction>

  • Type Parameters:
    F - the AggregationFunction this row contains
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDBAggregationFunctionRow, AggregationMethodDecorator, ColumnAggregator, DataTypeAggregator, DBColumnAggregationFunctionRow, DBDataTypeAggregationFunctionRow, DBPatternAggregationFunctionRow, NamedAggregationOperator, PatternAggregator

    public interface AggregationFunctionRow<F extends AggregationFunction>
    Interface that describes a row in an AggregationFunction table. It provides functions to check if the row is valid and the missing cell handling.
    Since:
    2.11
    Author:
    Tobias Koetter, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland
